{"tid":196565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沒有支那人是無辜】聯航CEO內部信曝光　華裔乘客「挑釁好鬥」","createTime":"2017-04-11T11:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T13:00:34.000Z","uid":79945,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92b6c8096e2fb41e9026a9c4bbb3a5e9f045713a","tid":196565,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=242100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D242100&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=cb35d5d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D242100&h=3dc37012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=242100</a> <br />\n<br />\n美國聯合航空（United Airlines）3411號班機因超賣機位，強硬要求4名旅客下機，一名華裔乘客不願放棄機位而抵抗，被航警拉扯掛彩流血，最後被強拖下飛機。聯航執行長穆尼奧斯（Oscar Munoz）除了對外發表道歉聲明，透過內部信告知員工，該名華裔乘客是「挑釁好鬥」，對一線人員作法表示支持。 <br />\n<br />\n穆尼奧斯在內部信表示，自己對於3411號班機發生糾紛感到困擾，尤其華裔乘客不配合下機的行為。而機組人員通知航警的決定，穆尼奧斯認為一線人員處理方式符合SOP，堅定支持機組人員的做法，最後也要求一線人員正常執行飛行任務。"},{"pid":"f5f13515d0fc3e76b7b0b4a7ac295b6e2468f3a5","tid":196565,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"而對於3411號班機糾紛，聯航員工亦描述了事件經過： <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 4月9日，3411號班機機位滿載，聯航臨時需要額外讓4位工作人員登機。 <br />\n<br />\n2.聯航提供高達1000美元的自願下機補償金，但仍無人願意下機，隨後被抽中須下機的華裔乘客開始提高音量，拒絕服從機組人員的指示下機。 <br />\n<br />\n3.經過多次交涉，這名華裔乘客變得越來越「擾亂秩序與挑釁好鬥」。 <br />\n<br />\n4.機組人員只能請來航警協助，但該名乘客仍不斷重覆拒絕下機。 <br />\n<br />\n5.航警無法取得該名乘客的合作之下，只得強行拖行他下機，過程中該名乘客仍持續反抗，甚至一度跑回機艙內。"},{"pid":"efbe9e85956cce270aa0afa2779edad4cd18973b","tid":196565,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/04/11/871790-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F871790-XXL.jpg&h=5ce028a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n▲聯航CEO給員工的內部信"},{"pid":"98be698325497cda96f583fff83fd85f013c9bce","tid":196565,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/04/11/871789-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F871789-XXL.jpg&h=1cdfcbb0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n▲聯航給員工的內部信"},{"pid":"224f90be13b09ffc99ddf7bfb14aa588c62b4690","tid":196565,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"聯航不了"},{"pid":"7a316f0e3e3d483c81cdf97ee21aa9fdaca32564","tid":196565,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:47:57.000Z","msg":"簡單講 <br />\n<br />\n人地比1000美金你落機，你唔肯 <br />\n<br />\n你比人抽中，去到人地地方，唔服從遊戲規則，唔肯落機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">總結：沒有一個支那人是無辜</span>"},{"pid":"99e89866a319a1fd0621487b129650ac0b771508","tid":196565,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:48:26.000Z","msg":"希望呢個post可以正視聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf3cedd24b29b6255d4c6001c55d8ae1a0c1dec","tid":196565,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望呢個post可以正視聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正左咩視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683adaff253122540534f0f7d4f19311f88efcd1","tid":19656